</taxonomicNameLabel>
in having the epandrium fused to hypandrium (
<figureCitation box="[416,509,1925,1950]" captionStart="FIGURES 22 – 27" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1939,1962]" captionTargetBox="[208,1378,197,1918]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[208,1379,193,1919]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 22 – 27. Hemerodromia cummingi sp. nov., holotype ♂. 22, habitus, lateral view; 23, wing. 24, terminalia, lateral view; 25, terminalia, dorsal view; 26, terminalia, ventral view; 27, hypandrium, phallus and epandrium, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233676/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="212">Figs 26</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[527,558,1925,1950]" captionStart="FIGURES 51 – 55" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1938,1961]" captionTargetBox="[211,1376,193,1912]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[210,1377,193,1917]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 51 – 55. Hemerodromia ubajaraensis sp. nov., holotype ♂. 51, habitus, lateral view; 52, terminalia, lateral view; 53, ejaculatory apodeme, subepandrial sclerite and surstylus, dorsal view; 54, gonocoxal apodeme, hypandrium and phallus, lateral view; 55, epandrium and hypandrium, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233680/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="212">55</figureCitation>
), subepandrial sclerite without posterior process and ejaculatory apodeme unilamellar flattened anteroposteriorly (
<figureCitation box="[618,704,1961,1986]" captionStart="FIGURES 22 – 27" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1939,1962]" captionTargetBox="[208,1378,197,1918]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[208,1379,193,1919]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 22 – 27. Hemerodromia cummingi sp. nov., holotype ♂. 22, habitus, lateral view; 23, wing. 24, terminalia, lateral view; 25, terminalia, dorsal view; 26, terminalia, ventral view; 27, hypandrium, phallus and epandrium, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233676/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="212">Figs 26</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[723,754,1961,1986]" captionStart="FIGURES 51 – 55" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1938,1961]" captionTargetBox="[211,1376,193,1912]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[210,1377,193,1917]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 51 – 55. Hemerodromia ubajaraensis sp. nov., holotype ♂. 51, habitus, lateral view; 52, terminalia, lateral view; 53, ejaculatory apodeme, subepandrial sclerite and surstylus, dorsal view; 54, gonocoxal apodeme, hypandrium and phallus, lateral view; 55, epandrium and hypandrium, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233680/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="212">53</figureCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName box="[781,1110,1962,1986]" class="Insecta" family="Empididae" genus="Hemerodromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="212" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ubajaraensis" status="sp. nov.">
